\c 6
\s Jesu Ishe wesabata
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika nesabata rechipiri shure kwerekutanga, achigura nemuminda yezviyo, vadzidzi vake vatanha hura, vakadya, vachi\add dzi\add*pukuta nemaoko.
\v 2 Asi vamwe vevaFarisi vakati kwavari: Munoitirei zvisiri pamutemo kuita nemasabata?
\v 3 Zvino Jesu achivapindura, wakati: Hamuna kuverenga kunyange Dhavhidhi zvaakaita, paakange ava nenzara iye nevakange vanaye,
\v 4 kuti wakapinda sei mumba maMwari, akatora akadya zvingwa zvekuratidza, akapavo vakange vanaye; izvo zvisiri pamutemo kudyiwa asi nevapristi vega?
\v 5 Ndokuti kwavari: Mwanakomana wemunhu ndiIshe wesabatawo.
\s Jesu unoporesa munhu waiva neruoko rwakawonyana
\p
\v 6 Zvino zvakaitikawo nerimwe sabata kuti wakapinda musinagoge, akadzidzisa; zvino kwakange kune munhu ipapo weruoko rwake rwerudyi rwakawonyana.
\v 7 Vanyori nevaFarisi vakamutarisisa, \add kuona\add* kana angaporesa nesabata, kuti vawane mhosva yavangamupomera.
\v 8 Asi iye wakaziva mifungo yavo, akati kumunhu wakange ane ruoko rwakawonyana: Simuka, uende unomira pakati. Akasimuka akamira.
\v 9 Zvino Jesu akati kwavari: Ndichakubvunzai \add chimwe\add* chinhu: Zviri pamutemo here nemasabata kuita zvakanaka kana kuita zvakaipa? Kuponesa upenyu kana kuparadza?
\v 10 Zvino akaringa-ringa kwavari vese, akati kumunhu: Tambanudza ruoko rwako. Akaita saizvozvo ruoko rwake rwukaporeswa rukagwinya serumwe.
\v 11 Ivo vakazara neupengo; vakataurirana umwe neumwe, kuti vangamuitei Jesu.
\s Jesu unodana vadzidzi vake
\p
\v 12 Zvino zvakaitika nemazuva iwayo kuti wakabuda akaenda kugomo kundonyengetera; agara usiku hwose mukunyengetera kuna Mwari.
\v 13 Zvino kwakati kwaedza, akadanira vadzidzi vake kwaari; akasanangura kwavari gumi nevaviri, vaakatumidzawo \add kuti\add* vaapositori;
\v 14 Simoni, waakatumidzawo Petro, naAndiriya munun'una wake, Jakobho naJohwani, Firipi naBhatoromiyo,
\v 15 Matewu naTomasi, Jakobho waArifiyosi, naSimoni wainzi Ziroti;
\v 16 Judhasi waJakobho, naJudhasi Isikariyoti, wakazovawo mutengesi.
\p
\v 17 Akaburuka navo, akamira pakaenzana, nechaunga chevadzidzi vake, nechaunga chikuru chavanhu vaibva Judhiya rose neJerusarema, nepagungwa reTire neSidoni, vakauya kuzomunzwa, nekuporeswa pazvifo zvavo;
\v 18 nevakange vachitambudziwa nemweya yetsvina, vakaporeswa.
\v 19 Chaunga chose chikatsvaka kumunyangata; nekuti kwakabuda simba kwaari rikaporesa vese.
\s Mharidzo yaJesu
\p
\v 20 Ndokusimudzira meso ake kuvadzidzi vake, akati: Makaropafadzwa varombo, nekuti ushe hwaMwari ndohwenyu.
\v 21 Makaropafadzwa imwi munenzara zvino, nekuti muchagutiswa. Makaropafadzwa imwi munochema ikozvino, nekuti muchaseka.
\v 22 Makaropafadzwa, kana vanhu vachikuvengai, uye kana vachikusarurai, vachikunyombai, vachirasha zita renyu serakashata, nekuda kweMwanakomana wemunhu.
\v 23 Farai nezuva iro, muuruke nemufaro; nekuti tarirai, mubairo wenyu mukuru kudenga; nekuti saizvozvo \add ndizvo\add* zvakaita madzibaba avo kuvaporofita.
\v 24 Asi mune nhamo imwi vakafuma! Nekuti magamuchira nyaradzo yenyu.
\v 25 Mune nhamo imwi munoguta! Nekuti muchanzwa nzara. Mune nhamo imwi munoseka zvino! Nekuti muchachema nekuwungudza.
\v 26 Mune nhamo kana vanhu vese vachitaura zvakanaka pamusoro penyu! Nekuti madzibaba avo akaita saizvozvo kuvaporofita venhema.
\v 27 Asi ndinoti kwamuri munonzwa: Idai mhandu dzenyu, itai zvakanaka kune vanokuvengai,
\v 28 ropafadzai vanokutukai, munyengeterere vanokubatai zvakaipa.
\v 29 Kune unokurova padama, umupe rimwewo; unokutorera nguvo yako, usarambidza neshati yako.
\v 30 Asi upe umwe neumwe unokumbira kwauri; neunokutorera zvako, usazvirevazve.
\v 31 Sezvamunoda kuti vanhu vaite kwamuri, imwi muvaitirewo saizvozvo.
\v 32 Uye kana muchida avo vanokudai, mune kuvongwa kwakadini? Nekuti vatadziwo vanoda vanovada.
\v 33 Uye kana muchiitira zvakanaka kune avo vanokuitirai zvakanaka, mune kuvongwa kwakadini? Nekuti vatadzi vanoitawo izvozvo.
\v 34 Uye kana muchikweretesa vamunotarisira kugamucira kwavari, mune kuvongwa kwakadini? Nekuti vatadzi vanokweretesawo vatadzi, kuti vagamuchirezve zvakaenzana nazvo.
\v 35 Asi idai vavengi venyu, muite zvakanaka, mukweretese musingatarisirizve chinhu; zvino mubairo wenyu uchava mukuru, mugova vana veWokumusoro-soro; nekuti iye unemoyo munyoro kune vasingavongi nevakaipa.
\v 36 Naizvozvo ivai netsitsi, sababa venyuwo vane tsitsi.
\v 37 Musatonga, mugorega kutongwawo; musapa mhosva, mugorega kupiwawo mhosva; regererai, mugoregererwawo.
\v 38 Ipai, mugopiwawo; chiyero chakanaka, chakatsikirirwa, nekuzunguzirwa, chinopfachukira vachakupai pachifuva chenyu. Nekuti nechiyero ichocho chamunoyera nacho muchayerwa nacho zvekare.
\p
\v 39 Akataura mufananidzo kwavari \add akati\add*: Kuti bofu ringatungamirira bofu here? Ko haangawiri mugomba ari maviri here?
\v 40 Mudzidzi haasi pamusoro pemudzidzisi wake; asi umwe neumwe kana apedzeredzwa uchava somudzidzisi wake.
\p
\v 41 Uye unotarirei rubanzu ruri muziso reumwe wako, asi danda riri muziso rako pachako haurinanzereri?
\v 42 Kana unogona kureva sei kune umwe wako, \add uchiti\add*: Umwe wangu, rega ndibudise rubanzu ruri muziso rako, iwe pachako usingaoni danda riri muziso rako? Iwe munyepedzeri, budisa pakutanga danda kubva muziso rako, zvino ipapo uchaona zvakanaka kubudisa rubanzu ruri muziso reumwe wako.
\p
\v 43 Nekuti hausi muti wakanaka unobereka chibereko chakaipa; kana muti wakaipa unobereka chibereko chakanaka.
\v 44 Nekuti muti umwe neumwe unozikamwa nechibereko chawo pachawo. Nekuti pamhinzwa, havatanhi maonde, kana parukato kutanha mazambiringa.
\v 45 Munhu wakanaka kubva pafuma yakanaka yemoyo wake unobudisa zvakanaka, nemunhu wakaipa kubva pafuma yakaipa yemoyo wake unobudisa zvakaipa; nekuti kubva pazvizere mumoyo make muromo wake unotaura.
\s Mufananidzo weimba yakavakwa paruware
\p
\v 46 Zvino munondiidzirei Ishe, Ishe, musingaiti zvinhu zvandinoreva?
\v 47 Ani nani unouya kwandiri akanzwa mashoko angu akaaita, ndichakuratidzai kuti wakafanana nani;
\v 48 wakafanana nemunhu wakavaka imba, akachera akadzikisa, akateya nheyo paruware; zvino mafashame akati auya, rukova rukarova zvine simba paimba iyo, rukasagona kuizunungusa; nekuti yakange yakateyiwa paruware.
\v 49 Asi unonzwa asingaiti, wakafanana nemunhu wakavaka imba pavhu isina nheyo; ipo rukova rwakarova nesimba, pakarepo ikawa, kuwa kweimba iyo kukava kukuru.
